OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,FWarning: Distressing content
OL,8,FA man who brutally stabbed his ex-
OL,9,Fpartner almost two dozen times in
OL,10,Ffront of her children has been jailed
OL,11,Ffor 22 years and four months.
OL,13,FJake Bamber, aged 35, had broken into
OL,14,Fthe victim's home armed with knives
OL,15,Fand hidden in a cupboard before
OL,16,Fleaping out and attacking her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,FInvestigators said he attacked her so
OL,7,Fviciously that he broke the knives;
OL,8,Fthis resulted in him going to the
OL,9,Fkitchen and re-arming himself to
OL,10,Fcontinue the attack before fleeing the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Carol Kirk,
OL,14,Fthe senior investigating officer,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This was a truly horrific and
OL,16,Fsenseless act of violence on a young
OL,17,Fwoman in her own home.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,F"The extreme level of brutality Bamber
OL,7,Finflicted on the victim was beyond
OL,8,Fbelief, and it was all because she had
OL,9,Fthe courage to end the cycle of
OL,10,Fdomestic abuse that he had subjected
OL,11,Fher to over an extended period of
OL,12,Ftime."
OL,14,FAt around 5.49pm on 10 January 2026, a
OL,15,F999 call was made requesting an urgent
OL,16,Fambulance and police attendance at an
OL,17,Faddress on Lindley Road in York.
OL,19,FWhen they arrived they found a woman
OL,20,Fconscious but with significant blood
OL,21,Floss due to her injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,FShe was able to identify her attacker
OL,7,Fas Bamber, her former partner.
OL,9,FThe victim was taken to hospital by
OL,10,Fambulance in a life-threatening
OL,11,Fcondition whilst an urgent search for
OL,12,FBamber commenced.
OL,14,FAt 9.35pm, Bamber was located
OL,15,Fcollapsed on Whitley Close in York,
OL,16,Fcovered in blood and unresponsive.
OL,18,FParamedics identified stab wounds, and
OL,19,Fhe was taken to hospital in a critical
OL,20,Fcondition. These injuries are
OL,21,Fsuspected to have been self-inflicted.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,FTwo days later on Monday 12 January,
OL,7,Fwhen Bamber was deemed medically fit,
OL,8,Fhe was arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fattempted murder and being in
OL,10,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,12,FThe next day, he was charged with
OL,13,Fthese offences, along with controlling
OL,14,Fand coercive behaviour between July
OL,15,F2023 and November 2025, and stalking
OL,16,Fbetween late November 2025 and early
OL,17,FJanuary 2026.
OL,19,FDCI Kirk said: "I commend the strength
OL,20,Fand bravery of the victim who, in my
OL,21,Feyes, is a true survivor.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,F"Even though she was desperately
OL,7,Finjured, her first thought was to
OL,8,Fprotect her young children and she
OL,9,Ftold them what to do to call for help.
OL,11,F"I am in awe of the courage of her
OL,12,Fchildren who despite being only young
OL,13,Fand terrified, stayed calm and
OL,14,Flistened to their mum so they could
OL,15,Fraise the alarm by calling for help
OL,16,Fboth on the phone and out of the
OL,17,Fwindow.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1776103864
OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner 22 times in
OL,4,Cfront of her children jailed
OL,6,F"I also pay tribute to her neighbour
OL,7,Fwho did not hesitate when the children
OL,8,Fyelled for help. The neighbour climbed
OL,9,Fthrough the window to get the children
OL,10,Fto safety, and started lifesaving
OL,11,Ffirst aid whilst not knowing if Bamber
OL,12,Fwas still in the house.
OL,14,F"In my mind, these women and children
OL,15,Fare true heroes."
OL,17,FOn Friday 10 April at York Crown Court
OL,18,FBamber was jailed for 22 years and
OL,19,Ffour months, and issued with an
OL,20,Fextended licence period of five years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
